PUSHER_KEY=your-pusher-key
PUSHER_SECRET=your-pusher-secret
PUSHER_CLUSTER=ap2
NODE_ENV=production
```

For frontend (VITE variables):
```
VITE_PUSHER_KEY=your-pusher-key
VITE_PUSHER_CLUSTER=ap2
```

